data.description: This home is perfect for anyone who loves spending time outdoors. With views of the golf course and swimming pool, as well as a private yard and three balconies, there is plenty of space to enjoy the fresh air. The gazebo is perfect for entertaining, and the downstairs apartment has its own washer and dryer, making it perfect for guests or extended family. This home is loaded with potential and won't be on the market for long- schedule a showing today! The listing broker's offer of compensation is made only to participants of the MLS where the listing is filed.
